b'Sustainability'
b'Sustainability'
b'UIC is working toward a greener world through recycling, improved transportation and energy efficiency. UIC has four climate commitments: carbon neutral campus, zero waste campus, net zero water campus and biodiverse campus.'
b'UIC is recognized by the Arbor Day Foundation as a Tree Campus! Learn more \xe2\x80\x94 volunteers welcome \xe2\x80\x94 from the Office of Sustainability.'
b'Office of Sustainability'
